snippet.title: Amber Heard trying to silence ppl #JusticeForJohnny #Imnotabot #Wejustdontlikeyou// follow up //
snippet.description:
Here's a follow up to my first reaction video talking about Amber Heard's defense team counterclaim calling some fans bots. And saying how people aren't believing "her truth." I look at the twitter accounts from the counterclaim (which mostly promote Johnny as a fan page) 

I feel like I could keep talking about this all day long and how the evidence shows that Amber is guilty of being the problem. 

I did write a blog post after my video to understand my feelings on why I don't trust her "story" https://afriendorfoe.home.blog/2020/08/21/heavy-on-my-heart-im-not-a-bot/

I stand with Johnny and THE truth. He is a victim and the evidence proves that. #JusticeforJohnny #WejustdontlikeyouAmber
